[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "……ということがありまして、レスナさんが僕の呪いを\n癒してくれたんです。まだ完全には解けていませんが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00121",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "は～……そんな薬まで調合できるなんて\nやっぱレスナってすごいんだなぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00122",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "今の話をレスナが聞いていたら、\nそんなことはないと謙遜するだろうが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00123",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "彼女は紛れもなくティムの命の恩人だ。\n受けた恩はなんとしてでも返したい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00124",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "うん。それにレスナさんについてけば\n色んな外の世界を見られそうだしね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00125",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "それは確かに。保証できちゃう。\nアタシも出会ってから知らない世界ばかり見てるし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00126",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "知らない海、知らない場所、知らない敵……\n色々経験を積んで、強くなりたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00127",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "今まで迷惑かけた分、兄さんを守れるくらいに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00128",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ああ……ティムよ、なんと嬉しいことを\n言ってくれるんだ、お前は……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00129",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "大切な家族を守りたい、そのために強くなりたい……\n分かる。私も姉様を守りたいし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_00130",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うんうん、アタシはベップに守られてるよね。\nもうちょっと、自分でしっかりしないとなんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00131",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "どんな姉様だとしても、姉様のベップはどこまでも\nずっと一緒にいるから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_00132",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "素敵な姉妹ですね。その想いの強さがあれば、\nきっと離れることはないと思いますよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00133",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "む。兄弟愛の強さなら俺も負けはしない。\nティムには俺がついている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_00134",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "なんかティムを見てると\n他人とは思えなくなってくるんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00135",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ティム、別に敬語じゃなくてもいいからね？\n親しみやすいアルビちゃんで売り出してもいるし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00136",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "わ、分かりました。とはいえ難しいな。言葉遣い、\n交じるかもしれません。あぁもう交じってる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_00137",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "仲が良すぎるのも大変かもだけど、\nやっぱり兄弟仲がいいのが一番よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00138",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "こっちはいつの間にやら９人兄弟の一員だけど、\n最近はドンパチ兄弟ゲンカしてるし？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00139",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "記憶にないのに兄弟って言われて、\nどんな感じ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00140",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "向こうは知ってて、こっちは知らないってのは\nやっぱりなんか変な感じね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00141",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "たとえば私はナナ……７番目だから\n４番目のシトリンは姉……兄？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00142",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ん？　なになに？\n僕のこと、呼んだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00143",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "シトリン、あんたって私のお姉ちゃんなの？\nそれともお兄ちゃん？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00144",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ふっふっふ。さあね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00145",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ダメダメ、こいつに聞いてもまともに返ってこない。\nこの前は「性別はシトリンさ」とか言ってたし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00146",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "謎があったほうが人生、ちょっぴり面白いんだって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00147",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "たび重なる記憶喪失で自分に謎が増えまくってる\n私の前で、よくそれを言い切れるわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00148",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そういえば見た感じ、アンタら九偉人の中で\n一番お姉さんなのはイェルカっぽいけど、違うのよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00149",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "そう、違う。上に長男と長女がいる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00150",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "名前、なんか１からもじったっぽいけど違った？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ああ、あれは勝手に名乗ってるだけ。\n元の名前はサンだって言ってた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "まあサンもといイェルカは、実際一番上っぽくしてて、\nこっちに世話焼いてくるけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00151",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "それがうざったいときもあるけど……\nなんだかんだ、かわいがってくれてるし嫌いじゃないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00152",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "３番目だからサン……ってことなのよね。\nそれじゃ１番目と２番目の二人は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00153",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "あの二人は……まぁ、ね。アレだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00154",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "は？　アレだからってなに？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00155",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "アレはアレ！　はい、それより魔物の出る海域だよ！\n襲ってくるから警戒しよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00156",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "くっ、魔物か。来い、怖くないったら怖くない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00157",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あからさまに話を逸らした……\nどんな兄と姉なのかしら……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00158",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]